  "texts": [
    "R3 notes: \"We have to establish that dialogue with them.",
    "They're not into reading consent forms, user agreements.",
    "So, we have to do the face to face dialogue and to explain to them.",
    "And some of them didn 't even realise what machine learning, AI, deep learning means.",
    "For them, it's like they think we're doing something robotics when we talk about AI."
  ]
